metadata.name: Floating Rocks
metadata.description:
Floating rocks came to mind during a lucid dream which the heavy objects might float in a mystical atmosphere.

This is a vision where anything can happen.

For the 1k landscape project to come, the highest bidder will have access to a high-resolution artwork plus various whitelists.

Collaboration with 𝔏𝔞+𝔠𝔥 who produced numerous soundtracks for a variety of famous artists, and his songs have been included on well-known auction houses such as Christie's, Sotheby's, Phillipps, and others.

Size of the artwork : 3840 x 2160 px
𝔏𝔞+𝔠𝔥 was in charge of the sound design.
